1 (d) Any position in which the applicant would be required to obtain a standard
2 fidelity bond or an equivalent bond, but would be disqualified from
3 obtaining such a bond due to a criminal conviction.
4 (5) This section does not prohibit an employer from notifying applicants that current
5 law or the employer's policy will disqualify an individual with a particular
6 criminal history background from employment in particular positions.
7 Section 2. This Act may be cited as the Ban the Box - The Criminal Record
8 Employment Discrimination Act.
